document_data.name: Liela
document_data.mainbody: '''Liela''' was a bureaucrat in [[Phlan]] in [[1489 DR]].
document_data.Personality: Liela's heart beat only for business. Everything in her office was placed to make her job more efficient. She spoke brusquely.
document_data.History: Liela was an employee of [[House Sokol]] at the administrative office that allowed access to [[Sokol Keep]].{{Cite adventurers league/Secrets of Sokol Keep|9-10}}
